-- Basic user-facing helpers inspired by common builtin functions.
-- This module only uses constructs currently supported by the language:
-- typed functions, generics, lists, tables, Option/Result, callbacks,
-- iterators, threads, atomics, and runtime builtins.

namespace basic {
